"Goood" Motormaster says to the small voice from Speedbreaker. He looked
around, and saw Dead-End fall. He walked over, reached down, and hoisted
him up. He then walked over to Switchblade. "Patch him up good enough to
continue" he said in his gruff voice. He turned around, and transformed.
Opening up his trailor, he reveiled certain robot parts. "Come on, you
can use some part to replace him" he said, motioning to an arm piece.
